---
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import { wedding } from '../data/wedding';
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="Travel & Lodging">
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Travel & Lodging"
    title="Transportation, lodging, and travel notes."
    copy="Everything we know so far about getting to Estes Park, finding a place to stay, and handling the mountain logistics."
  />

  <section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="section-shell grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-md bg-linen p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
        <p class="eyebrow">Getting here</p>
        <h2 class="section-h2">Denver International Airport</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/75">
          DIA is the closest major airport, about 1.5 hours away from Estes Park. You can rent a car or book a shuttle
          to take you to Estes Park. Estes Park Shuttle is the only shuttle service we currently know of. Check back soon
          for our Estes Park Shuttle 10% discount code.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-md bg-mist p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
        <p class="eyebrow">Hotels</p>
        <h2 class="section-h2">No hotel block. Staying at the Y recommended.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/75">
          We will not have a hotel block. We recommend staying at the YMCA not only for its proximity to our venue, but
          for the beautiful location surrounded by the National Park and many fun activities offered. However, if staying
          at the Y is not your preference, some good options in Estes Park include the iconic Stanley Hotel, the Outpost,
          or the Trailhead Lodge. Longmont or Loveland have many more affordable options, but are each about 45 minutes
          to 1 hour away by car.
        </p>
        <a class="button-secondary mt-8" href={wedding.travel.hotel.bookingUrl}>Search Hotels</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-linen py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="section-shell grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Airport</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.airport}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Parking</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.parking}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Transportation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.transportation}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Elevation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.elevation}</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
